Class FileProcessor

java.lang.Object
FileProcessor
public class FileProcessor extends Object
The `FileProcessor` class is responsible for processing input files related to election data, reading and updating election objects, and creating audit files. It contains methods for reading headers, creating candidates and parties, and handling the remaining lines forIR (Instant Runoff), OPL (Open Party List) and MPO (Multiple Popularity Only) elections.
